#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Distributor" field of the "Staff" table</h2>
The Distributor field will always remain the same for a staff member, containing the
name of the base of operations that they provides services for.  Staffers may
get shifted from route to route, but they will usually remain
under the same distributor.
<p>Are their exceptions?  Sure, the author of this documentation works for multiple
distributors.

